{
  "stem": "5313.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A couple of friend of mine which was, again, black marketing and they had some coffee and cigarette getting from camp to camp.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And on the way to Hamburg, the German, they caught him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they came back to the camp and told them that the German took away from them the whole carload of cigarette and coffee.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And without thinking twice, you know, I dressed up, you know, in an English uniform, which we had a certain uniform in the camp as a police chief.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my men, we had some uniforms similar to the English.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I dressed up as an English officer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I took two of my other people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We also dressed up in an English uniform.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we went up to Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we went into the police station.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We will find out where is they took the coffee and the cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we went in and I told them, you know, lock the door.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it was about six German police at the time in a police station there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I told them that who was the guy who took away the cigarette and the coffee.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And, anyway, make it short, we started and we opened all the jail doors and we let everybody-- we didn't even know German, not German.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We let everybody out of there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they find out, you know, that in a back room, it was the coffee and the cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They still had a lot of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They split it up between them, between themselves.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And about two hours later, we find out that the English police came, you know, and caught us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they told us what was doing here, you know, and we had no right to do this.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So they put us into a jail.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
